snippet.title: Wizards:Home Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official Wizards:Home Trailer. The game will feature over 100+ levels filled with fun biomes.  Local Co-op Multiplayer and many more features.  Be sure to look out for the PC, Mac, Linux build as well as being on the Nintendo Platform.  We will be shooting for a Xbox One Release.

Be sure to check out our social Media:

Wildcard Studios: www.wildcardstudios.org
FB: https://www.facebook.com/WizardsHome/
